<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="11Jul1938"><font color="red">11 July 1938</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I have received &hellip; the packet &hellip; I am glad to see that it includes a few sheets of Part IV in manuscript and hope that this concluding part of the book will progress steadily and smoothly in spite of the immense amount of work being done concurrently on the proofs of the earlier parts. </div>
